These are not the best times for Chichi Igbo as she has lost a family member who was very dear to her. Popular Nigerian female ex-footballer, Chichi Igbo has been thrown into mourning over the passing of her sister. The retired Danish Nigerian footballer took to Instagram to share a photo of her late sister with the caption, “sisterless” and a broken heart emoji. Chified, as she is fondly called, also took down every single photo previously shared on her Instagram and only left blank photos and candlelight photos to mourn her sister. Chichi Igbo got popular on social media after sharing sultry pictures and declaring that she is a lesbian. Source